<i> Weiwei, you're online? </i>

39
00:03:09,710 --> 00:03:12,560
Nini, you're here, too. What a coincidence!

40
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:15,230
<i> Diemeng, haven't seen you for so long.</i>

41
00:03:15,230 --> 00:03:16,920
<i> Yeah, work's too busy. </i>

42
00:03:16,920 --> 00:03:21,620
<i> Weiwei, you've been gone for ages, too, not just Diemeng.</i>

43
00:03:21,620 --> 00:03:24,570
<i>Yup, I've been busy with work, too.</i>

44
00:03:24,570 --> 00:03:27,270
<i>I've been interning lately.</i>

45
00:03:27,270 --> 00:03:29,210
