46
00:03:29,210 --> 00:03:31,920
<i> Eh. It's rare for the three of us to get together.</i>

47
00:03:31,920 --> 00:03:34,610
<i> How about if we go to the dungeon?</i>

48
00:03:35,630 --> 00:03:37,110
<i> Sure. </i>

49
00:03:37,110 --> 00:03:41,050
<i>I haven't played in a while and maybe a little rusty with the control.</i>

50
00:03:41,050 --> 00:03:44,430
<i> That's no problem. Let's first do one with medium difficulty to warm up. </i>

51
00:03:44,430 --> 00:03:47,990
<i> In any case, with Weiwei here, we'll definitely beat it. </i>

52
